Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兄弟以前會在這里玩\N{\fs14}This is where your brother used to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前會推他蕩秋千\N{\fs14}You used to push him on the swings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母不記得他 但你記得\N{\fs14}Your parents don't remember him, but you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道丹尼爾的事 \N{\fs14}How do you know about Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意跟我來嗎 \N{\fs14}Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 杰伊\N{\fs14}Hello, Jay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰  我的兄弟呢 \N{\fs14}Who are you? Where's my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被他們找到的人 我們也無計可施\N{\fs14}There's nothing we can do for the ones they've already found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們‥他們是誰 \N{\fs14}They? Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兄弟想警告你提防的人\N{\fs14}The people your brother tried to warn you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶走他的人\N{\fs14}The people that took him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們做的事 不是對我們所有人都管用\N{\fs14}What they do, it doesn't work on all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得走了\N{\fs14}We need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}＂偵測到叛逃可能＂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開始質疑事情 你的行為出現問題\N{\fs14}You've been asking questions. Your behavior's become problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會發現的 可能已經發現了\N{\fs14}They will notice, if they haven't already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你還剩多少時間 除非你跟我們走\N{\fs14}I don't know how much time you have unless you come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢下來 融入群眾 大家在看我們\N{\fs14}Slow down. Blend in. People are looking at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 \N{\fs14}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要來了\N{\fs14}They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動\N{\fs14}Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑\N{\fs14}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這里待個兩天 等到能夠安全上路\N{\fs14}We'll be here for a day or two, 'til it's safe to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位\N{\fs14}Hey, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是杰伊\N{\fs14}This is Jay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嗨 -嗨\N{\fs14}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你找個睡袋吧\N{\fs14}Let's get you a sleeping bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這不好受\N{\fs14}It's hard, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情我們無法補救 即便我們很想\N{\fs14}There's some things we can't fix, much as we want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fs14}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天好勇敢\N{\fs14}You were so brave today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起你父親\N{\fs14}You reminded me of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會很欣慰\N{\fs14}He really would've been proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間快到了\N{\fs14}It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去吧\N{\fs14}Okay. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他我愛他\N{\fs14}Tell him I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎 \N{\fs14}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟我爸爸打招呼嗎 \N{\fs14}You wanna say hi to my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸在哪里 \N{\fs14}Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他得去幫忙戰斗\N{\fs14}He had to leave to go help fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他答應過會回來\N{\fs14}But he promised to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我是法蘭琪 你收到嗎 \N{\fs14}Dad, this is Frankie, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天帶回來一個離群者\N{\fs14}We brought in a new outlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經喜歡他了\N{\fs14}I like him already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想要個哥哥\N{\fs14}I always wanted a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嘿 -別那樣叫我\N{\fs14}- Hey! - Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你哥哥\N{\fs14}I'm not your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留這種訊息沒有意義\N{\fs14}There's no point in leaving these messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸已經不在了\N{\fs14}Your dad is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟我真正的兄弟一樣\N{\fs14}Just like my real brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你在嗎 \N{\fs14}Dad, are you out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近基地\N{\fs14}Approaching base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別輕舉妄動\N{\fs14}Don't try anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我何必 \N{\fs14}Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目標一樣 要重建她\N{\fs14}We both want the same thing, to rebuild her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才帶我到你的營地 不是嗎 \N{\fs14}That's why you're taking me to your camp, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自以為懂很多 是吧 \N{\fs14}You think you know a lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂你嗎 \N{\fs14}About you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直不太能掌握你的下一步\N{\fs14}I never quite know what you'll do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要帶我去的地方‥沒錯 我知道那里\N{\fs14}But the place you're taking me, yes, I know that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱勒\N{\fs14}<i>Caleb.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒\N{\fs14}<i>Wake up.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在在哪里 \N{\fs14}Where the hell am I now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在玩你的游戲 \N{\fs14}Playing another one of your games?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女兒呢 \N{\fs14}Where is my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的女兒‥講話一直跳針\N{\fs14}Your daughter... like a broken record.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是只有你失去親人 凱勒\N{\fs14}You're not the only one who's lost someone, Caleb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且‥你不告訴我 我又何必告訴你 \N{\fs14}Besides, why should I tell you anything when you won't tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你什么 \N{\fs14}Tell you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的族類 離群者\N{\fs14}Your kind, the outliers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是從你開始的\N{\fs14}It all started with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂\N{\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你們不一樣 我的族類是完美的\N{\fs14}Unlike yours, my kind is... perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不朽和理性都臻完美\N{\fs14}Perfectly immortal. Perfectly rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們卻在做出不理性的選擇\N{\fs14}And yet, they're making irrational choices...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇有限生命 用死亡玷污自己\N{\fs14}Choosing mortality, staining themselves with death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么讓他們這樣做的 \N{\fs14}How are you making them do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么會知道 \N{\fs14}How the hell am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經告訴過我\N{\fs14}Once you told me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能戰勝我寄生蟲的影響\N{\fs14}that you could fight off the effects of my parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你有我沒有的東西\N{\fs14}because you had something that I don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在當時就已經有所領悟\N{\fs14}You knew something, even then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么 \N{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恐怕記不得了\N{\fs14}I'm afraid I can't recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的對話不一定要是單方面\N{\fs14}This doesn't have to be a one-way street.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想提供你一點動機\N{\fs14}I'd like to offer you some incentive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了 凱勒 你已經死了很久\N{\fs14}You're dead, Caleb. You have been for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將你的心智 帶回來的這個身體是暫時的\N{\fs14}This body that I've brought your mind back into is temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它已經開始失靈\N{\fs14}It's already failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能只剩下兩天 還會愈來愈痛苦\N{\fs14}I doubt you have more than a couple increasingly painful days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我會把你丟掉 再重來一次\N{\fs14}Then I'll toss you away and start all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有解套的辦法\N{\fs14}But there is a way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能終止這酷刑\N{\fs14}An end to this torture...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要回答我的問題就好\N{\fs14}if you'd just answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找下一個人試試看吧\N{\fs14}Maybe you'll have better luck with the next guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不告訴我的話 也許你女兒會開口\N{\fs14}If you won't tell me, maybe your daughter will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪 她‥\N{\fs14}Frankie... she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還活著\N{\fs14}Alive, for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何微笑 \N{\fs14}Why are you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜她會比你快屈服\N{\fs14}I'm guessing she'll break a lot faster than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還活著\N{\fs14}She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒活著\N{\fs14}My girl is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你逮不到她 對吧 \N{\fs14}And you can't catch her, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不敢肯定\N{\fs14}I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:13:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我派了一個訪客去找她\N{\fs14}I sent a visitor... her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂玻璃 內部＂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你所剩的時間想想這件事吧\N{\fs14}Enjoy this knowledge while it lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給了你一條出路 凱勒\N{\fs14}I offered you a path out, Caleb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做出了選擇\N{\fs14}You made your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都是\N{\fs14}You all did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂\N{\fs14}Hey. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查繼電器 看其他人有沒有回報\N{\fs14}Check the relay. See if the others have called in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的腦袋能解答\N{\fs14}The answers to the questions
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我夜不成眠的問題\N{\fs14}that have kept me up at night are all in her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就喚醒她\N{\fs14}Then we'll wake her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你能問她\N{\fs14}And you can ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要先補給\N{\fs14}We'll need some supplies first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看來對這里很熟\N{\fs14}You seem to know a lot about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這園區和西部世界 是同一個設計師所建\N{\fs14}This park shares an architect with Westworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 \N{\fs14}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前在那里工作\N{\fs14}I used to work there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路小心\N{\fs14}Careful where you step.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這地方建得不是很牢靠\N{\fs14}This place wasn't built to last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當年在園區是做什么的 \N{\fs14}What did you do at the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我設計接待員的程式\N{\fs14}I programmed the hosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓機器人變得過于自主 害慘了這世界\N{\fs14}You gave the puppets strings long enough to strangle the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用意從來就不是那樣\N{\fs14}That was never the intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 但結果是如此\N{\fs14}No, but it was the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才能辨別出 \N{\fs14}So, that's how you were able to pick out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐館的接待員 \N{\fs14}those two hosts at the diner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本是本月最佳員工\N{\fs14}You're employee of the fucking month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海爾會需要你這樣的人\N{\fs14}Hale would've needed someone like you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫她傳播寄生蟲\N{\fs14}to help spread her parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有涉及這件事 \N{\fs14}Did you have anything to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 那是在我之后的事\N{\fs14}No, that was after my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但迪洛斯向來\N{\fs14}But Delos was notorious for keeping
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對員工和客人一樣隱瞞\N{\fs14}its employees as in the dark as the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時不太明白問題的復雜度\N{\fs14}I didn't always grasp the complexity of the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在最關心的\N{\fs14}but what I'm most concerned with now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是解決之道\N{\fs14}is the solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:16:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修復梅芙的身體還算單純\N{\fs14}Repairing Maeve's body will be relatively simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的心智就是另一回事\N{\fs14}Her mind is a different matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋在地下這么久 損毀了她的控制元件\N{\fs14}Being underground for so long has corrupted her control unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得拿另一個來替換\N{\fs14}We'll have to replace it with another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的就可以了\N{\fs14}His will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有電了\N{\fs14}We've got power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電線接到發電機\N{\fs14}Cables are connected to the generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這會管用嗎 \N{\fs14}You think this is gonna work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有六成的機率 她醒來后會接受我們的計劃\N{\fs14}Sixty percent of the time, she'll wake up amenable to our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的四成 \N{\fs14}The other 40%
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且說她有起床氣吧\N{\fs14}let's just say she wakes up on the wrong side of the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你何時會告訴我\N{\fs14}You ever gonna tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎有這種預知能力的 大預言家\N{\fs14}how you came up with these predictions, Nostradamus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老習慣\N{\fs14}Old habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源自多年來大量地跑機率演算法\N{\fs14}Comes from years of running probabilistic algorithms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當年建造原始園區和接待員的人\N{\fs14}The people who built the original park and hosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是在模擬環境中建造他們\N{\fs14}they started first by building them in a simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復制品\N{\fs14}A copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛蒂海爾做了一樣的事\N{\fs14}Charlotte Hale did the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來\N{\fs14}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舊園區\N{\fs14}In the old parks
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們用帽子收集資料\N{\fs14}they used hats to collect the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中的技術速度很慢\N{\fs14}The tech inside of them was slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以如今的標準來說很原始\N{\fs14}Primitive by today's standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要控制全世界\N{\fs14}To assume control of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海爾需要以更快的速度了解心智\N{\fs14}Hale needed to understand minds at a much faster rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她將其更新成了什么 \N{\fs14}So, she upgraded to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個無所不在的系統\N{\fs14}A ubiquitous system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初可說園區每個房間都有一個\N{\fs14}There was one in practically every room in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易隱藏\N{\fs14}Easily camouflaged
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它利用了人類最基本的沖動\N{\fs14}because it played off the most base human impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛榮\N{\fs14}Vanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過鏡子\N{\fs14}Through the looking glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧\N{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看看\N{\fs14}Take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在做什么 -重新格式化處理器\N{\fs14}- What are you doing? - Reformatting its processor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能快速處理大量資訊\N{\fs14}It can handle large amounts of information swiftly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣能幫我們加速 梅芙的資料傳輸\N{\fs14}which will help us speed up Maeve's data transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是梅芙的心智\N{\fs14}That's Maeve's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要花多久時間 \N{\fs14}How long is this going to take?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕會太久\N{\fs14}Too long, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友們很快會來\N{\fs14}Your friends will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能讓他們干預\N{\fs14}We can't let them interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fs14}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fs14}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂\N{\fs14}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪還活著 好嗎 \N{\fs14}Frankie is alive, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得逃出去\N{\fs14}I have to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的出路是‥\N{\fs14}The only way out is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡\N{\fs14}death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:22:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我不接受\N{\fs14}No! That's not good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡只是‥\N{\fs14}Dying is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始\N{\fs14}the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要‥燃燒\N{\fs14}You must... burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 \N{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你成功了 就跑\N{\fs14}If you succeed, you... run.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗的話 就躲起來\N{\fs14}If you fail, you... hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什么 \N{\fs14}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道‥\N{\fs14}I only know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴自己的事\N{\fs14}what I told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要‥\N{\fs14}You need...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間\N{\fs14}time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來 爸爸 跟你賽跑\N{\fs14}C'mon, Daddy! Race ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.91,0:24:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你決定重新加入我們了\N{\fs14}I see you've decided to rejoin us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回到這世界\N{\fs14}Welcome back to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.31,0:24:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂終結此版本＂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.33,0:25:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在現在嗎 \N{\fs14}Am I... Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.37,0:25:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肯定是近期我被問過\N{\fs14}That's certainly the most existential question
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.16,0:25:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最存在主義的問題\N{\fs14}someone's asked me recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.72,0:25:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道身在何處嗎 \N{\fs14}Do you know where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.31,0:26:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有沒有回來 \N{\fs14}Did she come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.06,0:26:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的‥朋友\N{\fs14}My... friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.15,0:26:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.03,0:26:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值了很長的班\N{\fs14}Long shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.28,0:26:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了你的布丁\N{\fs14}I ate your pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.91,0:26:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得回去拯救性命了\N{\fs14}Gotta get back to saving lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.18,0:26:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱勒\N{\fs14}Caleb...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.43,0:26:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你朋友沒有回來\N{\fs14}even if your friend doesn't come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.85,0:26:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要保持清醒\N{\fs14}stay awake anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.35,0:28:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽生病時 我什么都得替她做\N{\fs14}When my mom got sick, I had to do everything for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.61,0:28:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫她洗澡 喂她\N{\fs14}I washed her, fed her
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.44,0:28:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她無法喝東西后 拿冰塊擦她的嘴唇\N{\fs14}rubbed ice across her lips when she couldn't drink anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.53,0:28:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很小心\N{\fs14}I was careful
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.28,0:28:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想讓她受無謂的痛苦\N{\fs14}because I didn't want her to feel any more pain than she had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.99,0:28:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你在對她做的事\N{\fs14}Just like you're doing to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.33,0:28:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部分的程序需要巧手\N{\fs14}This part of the process requires a delicate hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.59,0:28:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她不是普通的接待員吧 \N{\fs14}But she's not an ordinary host, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.47,0:28:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識她\N{\fs14}You knew her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.14,0:28:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs14}I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.60,0:28:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最后一次見到我父親時 他就是和她在一起\N{\fs14}The last time I saw my father, he was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.52,0:28:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他再也沒回來\N{\fs14}And then he never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.18,0:28:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信她若得知你父親的下場 會極為心痛\N{\fs14}I'm sure it would pain her greatly to hear what happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.98,0:29:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道發生了什么事\N{\fs14}I want to know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.86,0:29:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有她不懂痛苦\N{\fs14}And she doesn't know pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.53,0:29:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都不懂\N{\fs14}None of them do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.53,0:29:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的感覺只是表象\N{\fs14}Feelings are just an affect to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.29,0:29:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以撥動的開關\N{\fs14}A switch that you can turn on and off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.66,0:29:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然只是一個選擇 就無法徹底地愛或失去\N{\fs14}You can't love or lose fully when it's just a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.71,0:29:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我對她沒有感情 不像你對她顯然有的\N{\fs14}So no, I don't have a soft spot for her like you apparently do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.63,0:29:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救世界 會產生奇妙的盟友\N{\fs14}Saving the world makes for strange bedfellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.02,0:29:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們回來了\N{\fs14}They're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.64,0:29:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們的時間可能到了\N{\fs14}Well, then our time may be up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.46,0:30:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是干嗎 \N{\fs14}What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.01,0:30:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們找到了武器\N{\fs14}We found the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.18,0:30:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個接待員 \N{\fs14}A fucking host?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.77,0:30:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很慘\N{\fs14}It was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.52,0:30:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們救出一個離群者 琳賽\N{\fs14}We got an outlier out, Lindsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.02,0:30:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什么事 \N{\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.19,0:30:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們似乎知道我們要來\N{\fs14}It's like they knew we were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.69,0:30:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的解釋\N{\fs14}And the only way that would've happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.86,0:30:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有人在為敵方當間諜\N{\fs14}is if someone was spying for the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.66,0:30:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召集所有人 該來找出答案了\N{\fs14}Gather everyone up. Time to find answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.04,0:30:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省省吧\N{\fs14}Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.75,0:30:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ｃ\N{\fs14}C!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.71,0:30:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內賊就在這里\N{\fs14}There's your mole.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.46,0:30:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是接待員\N{\fs14}He's a host.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.79,0:30:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就有兩個了\N{\fs14}Which makes two.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.71,0:30:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜\N{\fs14}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.17,0:30:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－這是什么  －對我的掃瞄\N{\fs14}- What is this? - A scan. Of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.55,0:30:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園區的設計 是為了搜集客人的資料\N{\fs14}The park was designed to collect data from guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.39,0:30:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想復制我們所有人\N{\fs14}He's trying to copy all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.89,0:30:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 \N{\fs14}You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.02,0:30:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很復雜\N{\fs14}It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.81,0:30:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得信任我\N{\fs14}You have to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.35,0:31:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是信你\N{\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.94,0:31:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信你在騙我\N{\fs14}I trust that you're lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.56,0:31:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙我們全部人\N{\fs14}To all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.69,0:31:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶他們出去\N{\fs14}Get them outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.21,0:31:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這接待員的控制元件呢 \N{\fs14}Where's this host's control unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.54,0:31:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還不能摧毀它\N{\fs14}We can't destroy it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.38,0:31:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－為何 －當中有關于我父親的資訊\N{\fs14}- Why not? - It has information about my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.67,0:31:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我得手 就可以殺光他們\N{\fs14}Once I have that, we can kill all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.06,0:33:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.73,0:35:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人出去 準備撤離\N{\fs14}Everyone out. Get ready to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.15,0:35:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這兩個找到了我們 那可能有更多要來\N{\fs14}If these two found us, more might be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.49,0:35:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不領情 我們是來幫你們的\N{\fs14}The unkindest cut of all. We came here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.41,0:35:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪\N{\fs14}Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.25,0:35:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這里自有原因\N{\fs14}You came here for your own reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.62,0:35:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要以我為主了\N{\fs14}And now mine takes priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.54,0:35:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道我父親發生了什么事\N{\fs14}I need to know what happened to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.92,0:35:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺過我很多次了 不會改變結果\N{\fs14}You've killed me many times. It doesn't change the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.17,0:35:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我殺了你朋友呢  會改變什么嗎 \N{\fs14}How 'bout I kill your friend. That change anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.21,0:35:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你得注意你的朋友們\N{\fs14}Right now, you need to focus on your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.68,0:35:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 為什么 \N{\fs14}Oh, yeah, why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.68,0:35:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們其中一人隱瞞了身份\N{\fs14}One of them isn't who they claim to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.47,0:35:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－有一個人會背叛你們 －胡說\N{\fs14}- One of them will betray you. - Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.93,0:35:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽他的吧\N{\fs14}Listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.02,0:35:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的預測往往是對的\N{\fs14}He's usually right about this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.48,0:35:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很欠揍但準確\N{\fs14}Really annoying but right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.11,0:35:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的 是誰 \N{\fs14}Fuck you. Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.15,0:35:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跑過所有可能的變化\N{\fs14}I've run all the possible iterations.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.19,0:36:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若能告訴你就好了\N{\fs14}I wish I could tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.66,0:36:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候是你女友歐迪娜\N{\fs14}Sometimes, it's your girlfriend, Odina.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.91,0:36:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候是杰伊或琳賽\N{\fs14}Sometimes it's Jay or Lindsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.91,0:36:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一次居然是史塔伯\N{\fs14}Hell, one time it was even Stubbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.67,0:36:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 別看我\N{\fs14}What? Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.04,0:36:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內賊還在潛伏 Ｃ\N{\fs14}The mole is still out there, C.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.96,0:36:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的團隊進入海爾的城市中心\N{\fs14}Your team went into the heart of Hale's city
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.17,0:36:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一個人沒回來\N{\fs14}but one of them didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.88,0:36:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－給我閉嘴 －我知道這很難接受\N{\fs14}- Shut the fuck up. - I know this is hard to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.55,0:36:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但所有可能性中 \N{\fs14}but there's not a single version
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.68,0:36:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一個是你們全部生還的\N{\fs14}where all of you make it out of here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.60,0:36:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你建議我怎么做 \N{\fs14}So, what do you suggest that I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.52,0:36:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須殺了他們其中一人\N{\fs14}You're going to have to kill one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.65,0:36:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則他們會殺了你\N{\fs14}Or they will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.45,0:36:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了\N{\fs14}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.49,0:36:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.38,0:37:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為能信任他\N{\fs14}I thought I could trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.89,0:37:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和你說你想聽的話\N{\fs14}He told you what you wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.10,0:37:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很難抵抗\N{\fs14}It's a hard thing to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.31,0:37:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你查出他的計劃了嗎 \N{\fs14}Did you find out what his plan is?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.90,0:37:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是更多的謎題\N{\fs14}Just more riddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.11,0:37:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少他不能再造成更多傷害了\N{\fs14}At least he can't do any more damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.66,0:37:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 Ｃ\N{\fs14}I don't know, C.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.41,0:37:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為還有內情\N{\fs14}I think there's something more going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.50,0:37:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定 這里不能信任的只有他們兩個\N{\fs14}I'm not sure the two of them are the only ones here we can't trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.71,0:37:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我們有人被轉化了 \N{\fs14}You think one of us was turned?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.79,0:37:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉化 被寄生 我不知道\N{\fs14}Turned, parasited, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.09,0:37:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們在那里分散了 隨時都可能發生\N{\fs14}But we were scattered out there. It could've happened any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.09,0:37:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們對這離群者 又知道多少 \N{\fs14}And what do we know about this new outlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.55,0:37:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許她本來就是個誘餌\N{\fs14}Maybe she was bait from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.56,0:37:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ｃ\N{\fs14}C...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.52,0:37:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我能信任的只有你\N{\fs14}Right now, you're the only one I can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.77,0:38:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒出那次任務\N{\fs14}You weren't on that mission. Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.32,0:38:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你從來不會只說我想聽的話\N{\fs14}you never just tell me what I wanna hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.36,0:38:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們怎么辦 \N{\fs14}So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.32,0:38:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況先繼續保密\N{\fs14}Keep this situation on lockdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.24,0:38:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳賽和其他人交給我\N{\fs14}Leave me to worry about Lindsay and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.66,0:38:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去視查一下防線 結束后來這里碰頭\N{\fs14}You do a sweep of our defenses. Meet here when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.71,0:38:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.02,0:38:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這么急著要去哪兒 \N{\fs14}Where are you going in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.69,0:38:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在跟蹤我 \N{\fs14}You following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.44,0:38:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我在找你\N{\fs14}No, I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.86,0:38:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎 \N{\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.20,0:38:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在提高警覺\N{\fs14}I'm just on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.95,0:38:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰伊要我再檢查一次防線\N{\fs14}Jay ordered me to double check the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.12,0:38:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝 怎么了 \N{\fs14}Look, baby, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.91,0:38:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變得怪怪的\N{\fs14}You're not acting like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.17,0:39:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我回來后 發現你在重建里面那東西\N{\fs14}And I come back to find you rebuilding that thing in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.42,0:39:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么 \N{\fs14}What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.96,0:39:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會問我她為何重要\N{\fs14}You wouldn't have to ask me why she was important.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.76,0:39:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你懂我的話\N{\fs14}Not if you knew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.68,0:39:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你夠了解了\N{\fs14}I know you well enough to know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.02,0:39:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以知道 你來這里不是在檢查防線\N{\fs14}you're not out here checking our perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.14,0:39:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要繼續把她重建完成\N{\fs14}You're gonna go finish rebuilding her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.36,0:39:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把她的腦藏在哪里 \N{\fs14}So, where'd you hide this host brain of hers?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.62,0:39:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 \N{\fs14}What the fuck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.16,0:39:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走就對了\N{\fs14}Just move.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.50,0:39:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－你以為我是內賊 －也許\N{\fs14}- You think I'm one of them? - Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.25,0:39:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你受到他們控制 你也不會知道\N{\fs14}Maybe you're under their control. You might not even know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.76,0:39:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N{\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.93,0:39:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你不是內賊 在這里也比較安全\N{\fs14}If you're not one of them, you'll be safer here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.78,0:40:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還在逃亡 但他逃不遠的\N{\fs14}He's still on the run, but he won't get far.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.95,0:40:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人類\N{\fs14}These humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.24,0:40:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可悲的抵抗\N{\fs14}Their petty defiances.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.54,0:40:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們做的所有事都好渺小 讓人精疲力竭\N{\fs14}Everything they do is so small, it's exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.72,0:40:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平常都待在城市\N{\fs14}You spend your days in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.77,0:40:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.90,0:40:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會不會‥\N{\fs14}Do they ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.86,0:40:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹惱你 \N{\fs14}get under your skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.74,0:40:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會接近離群者\N{\fs14}I don't get close to the outliers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.20,0:40:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡羊群\N{\fs14}I prefer the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.87,0:41:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了結這件事\N{\fs14}I'd like to put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.22,0:42:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡\N{\fs14}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.02,0:42:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fs14}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.48,0:42:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪還活著\N{\fs14}Hey, Frankie's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.57,0:42:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪 我得‥\N{\fs14}Frankie. I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.07,0:42:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得逃出這里\N{\fs14}I have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.37,0:42:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得找到她\N{\fs14}I need to reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.00,0:42:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我\N{\fs14}Use me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.18,0:42:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我\N{\fs14}Use me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.12,0:43:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起‥\N{\fs14}I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.77,0:43:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪 慢一點 等我\N{\fs14}<i>Hey, hey, Frankie, slow down!</i> <i>Wait for me.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.53,0:43:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fs14}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.28,0:43:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 \N{\fs14}Hey! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.32,0:43:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看你的膝蓋\N{\fs14}Let me see that knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.03,0:43:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的第一個戰斗傷疤\N{\fs14}It's your very first battle scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.70,0:43:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想試著走看看嗎 \N{\fs14}You want to try walking on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.20,0:43:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能\N{\fs14}It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.54,0:43:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有事是不可能的\N{\fs14}Hey. Nothing is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.92,0:43:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道哪種人不會被打敗嗎 \N{\fs14}You know what kind of person can't be beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.34,0:43:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放棄的那種人\N{\fs14}The kind that doesn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.26,0:44:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎 \N{\fs14}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.51,0:44:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 寶貝\N{\fs14}There you go, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.35,0:44:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.10,0:44:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇過她\N{\fs14}I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.53,0:45:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 \N{\fs14}Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.86,0:45:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我小時候\N{\fs14}When I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.16,0:45:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快忘了她的臉\N{\fs14}I had almost forgotten her face
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.75,0:45:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我從來沒忘記她奪走的東西\N{\fs14}but never forgot what she took from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.43,0:45:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ｃ 我知道你為何想喚醒她\N{\fs14}C, I know why you want to wake her up
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.02,0:45:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這太冒險了\N{\fs14}but it's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.81,0:45:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不知道他們打算拿她做什么\N{\fs14}We have no idea what they were planning with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.11,0:45:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一睜開眼就可能殺光我們\N{\fs14}She could kill us all the second she opens her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.61,0:45:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是會傳送訊息給我爸\N{\fs14}I still send him messages... My dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.87,0:45:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用無線電傳話到我們的舊頻率\N{\fs14}On the radio, to our old frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.25,0:45:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道以為他會聽到 根本就是瘋了\N{\fs14}And I know that it is crazy to think that he hears them
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.08,0:46:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要他有一點生還的可能 \N{\fs14}but if there is any chance that he's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.38,0:46:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就得知道\N{\fs14}I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.96,0:46:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要你受傷 Ｃ\N{\fs14}I don't want you to get hurt, C.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.26,0:46:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切只會揭開舊傷疤\N{\fs14}All this will do is rip open an old wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.64,0:46:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她無法帶你爸回來\N{\fs14}She can't bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.31,0:46:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得摧毀她的控制元件\N{\fs14}We have to destroy her control unit
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.82,0:46:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免得海爾利用她除掉我們\N{\fs14}before Hale uses her to take us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.60,0:46:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你爸還活著 我們會有別的辦法找到他\N{\fs14}And if your dad's out there, we'll find him another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.94,0:46:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起\N{\fs14}Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.03,0:46:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的家人 Ｃ\N{\fs14}You're my family, C.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.61,0:46:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就像我的妹妹\N{\fs14}You're like a sister to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.20,0:46:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能失去你\N{\fs14}I can't lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.67,0:46:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯納把她的控制元件放在樓下\N{\fs14}Bernard put her pearl downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.30,0:46:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧\N{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.22,0:46:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我知道這很難\N{\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.51,0:46:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們不能冒險\N{\fs14}I know this is hard but we can't take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.73,0:46:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.44,0:47:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰伊可能很欠揍 但至少他誠實\N{\fs14}Jay could be a dick, but at least he was honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.69,0:47:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從來不想當我的哥哥\N{\fs14}He never wanted to be my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.42,0:47:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的小家伙\N{\fs14}Poor little C.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.04,0:47:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在哭訴你家人的事\N{\fs14}Always whining about your fucking family.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.55,0:47:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲\N{\fs14}It's pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.89,0:47:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想殺你 Ｃ\N{\fs14}I don't wanna kill you, C.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.29,0:47:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是好消息 Ｃ\N{\fs14}This is good news, C.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.54,0:48:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅芙不知道你爸的事 但我知道\N{\fs14}Maeve doesn't know anything about your dad, but I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.92,0:48:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我她的控制元件在哪里\N{\fs14}Show me where her pearl is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.36,0:48:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告訴你想知道的一切\N{\fs14}and I'll tell you anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.38,0:48:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甭談判了\N{\fs14}Don't bother with the negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.17,0:48:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的話都不能信\N{\fs14}Everything you say is bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.45,0:48:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂錄制訊息中＂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.84,0:48:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小餅干\N{\fs14}Cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.67,0:48:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪\N{\fs14}Frankie. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.76,0:48:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你爸爸\N{\fs14}It's your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.22,0:48:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在\N{\fs14}I know you're out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.72,0:49:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你聽見了 我要你知道\N{\fs14}And if you're hearing this, I want you to know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.19,0:49:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會贏的\N{\fs14}you're going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.06,0:49:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會做到我做不到的事\N{\fs14}You're going to do what I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.53,0:49:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你很堅強\N{\fs14}because you are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.58,0:49:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我堅強太多了\N{\fs14}So much stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.87,0:49:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界\N{\fs14}This world...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.21,0:49:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她創造的這世界是個謊言\N{\fs14}This world she... she made is... it's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.59,0:49:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的\N{\fs14}It's not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.26,0:49:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你擁有的‥\N{\fs14}But what you... what you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.59,0:49:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你擁有的是真的\N{\fs14}What you have is... is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.14,0:49:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我失敗了\N{\fs14}I'm sorry that I failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.32,0:49:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我沒能陪伴你\N{\fs14}That I haven't been there for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.70,0:49:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉你得承擔這一切\N{\fs14}That now it has to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.08,0:50:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你辦得到\N{\fs14}But you can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.21,0:50:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的戰士\N{\fs14}You're my warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.51,0:50:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你\N{\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.93,0:50:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂傳送中＂
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.47,0:50:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂已傳送＂
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.73,0:50:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小餅干\N{\fs14}<i>Cookie.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.40,0:50:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪\N{\fs14}<i>Frankie. Hey.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.28,0:50:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你爸爸\N{\fs14}<i>It's your dad.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.49,0:50:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在\N{\fs14}<i>I know you're out there.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.45,0:50:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你聽見了 我要你知道\N{\fs14}<i>And if you're hearing this,</i> <i>I want you to know that...</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.25,0:50:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸\N{\fs14}Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.60,0:50:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會贏的\N{\fs14}<i>you're going to win.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.22,0:51:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我她的控制元件在哪里\N{\fs14}Tell me where her pearl is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.56,0:51:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的 我拿去\N{\fs14}Fuck you. I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.43,0:51:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏起來了\N{\fs14}I stashed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.98,0:51:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里 \N{\fs14}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.23,0:51:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背后\N{\fs14}Behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.99,0:51:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱勒‥\N{\fs14}Caleb...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.37,0:51:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了 \N{\fs14}I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.87,0:51:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他活著\N{\fs14}Alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.46,0:51:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是‥\N{\fs14}You're his...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.59,0:51:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他女兒\N{\fs14}His daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.47,0:51:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了\N{\fs14}Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.39,0:51:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人失望\N{\fs14}What a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.40,0:51:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等了好久 想知道你要跟女兒說什么\N{\fs14}I've waited such a long time to know what you had to tell your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.99,0:52:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你‥\N{\fs14}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.53,0:52:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我耐著性子等你回憶了幾百次\N{\fs14}Hundreds of times, I sat through your stupid memories
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.49,0:52:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能找到你特別之處的線索\N{\fs14}hoping to catch a single clue as to what makes you so special
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.41,0:52:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能如此抗拒我的命令\N{\fs14}so resistant to my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.50,0:52:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我啥都沒發現\N{\fs14}And I learned jack shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.79,0:52:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就想\N{\fs14}So, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.34,0:52:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你點希望 想必能讓你亮底牌\N{\fs14}nothing like a little hope to get you to show your cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.51,0:52:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比其他人都走得更遠\N{\fs14}You made it farther than any of the others
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.43,0:52:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果你只是浪費機會 做無謂的道歉\N{\fs14}and all you did was waste your shot on a worthless apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.89,0:52:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為說幾句話就能彌補\N{\fs14}You think a few words will make up
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.38,0:52:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多年前做的選擇\N{\fs14}for the choices you made all those years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.44,0:52:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不重要\N{\fs14}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.65,0:52:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訊息送出了\N{\fs14}It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.28,0:52:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒聽到\N{\fs14}She didn't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.74,0:52:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不需要聽到\N{\fs14}She doesn't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.33,0:52:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是會輸\N{\fs14}You're still going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.62,0:52:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有感染你的接待員\N{\fs14}We didn't infect your hosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.42,0:52:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是嘛\N{\fs14}You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.76,0:53:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰 \N{\fs14}Who did?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.55,0:53:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你\N{\fs14}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.10,0:53:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的接待員 \N{\fs14}Your hosts would rather die
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.64,0:53:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧死也不要活在你的世界\N{\fs14}than live in your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.19,0:53:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒有被感染\N{\fs14}They're not infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.69,0:53:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想逃離你\N{\fs14}They're just trying to get away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.60,0:54:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離開時\N{\fs14}When I left...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.47,0:54:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為是在給他一個機會\N{\fs14}I thought I was giving him a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.31,0:54:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到會導致這一切\N{\fs14}I didn't think it would lead to all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.03,0:54:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心里一部分在怪罪你\N{\fs14}Part of me blamed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.15,0:54:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一部分知道要是他還活著\N{\fs14}And part of me knew that if there was any chance he was alive
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.03,0:54:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因為你在他身邊\N{\fs14}it was because you were with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.37,0:54:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所做的一切\N{\fs14}Everything you guys did...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.33,0:54:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們在這里的原因\N{\fs14}that's why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.17,0:55:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么‥\N{\fs14}Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.46,0:55:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來把自己起頭的事做完吧\N{\fs14}let's finish what we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.56,0:56:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂第２７９版 準備列印＂
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.97,0:56:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱勒\N{\fs14}Caleb.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.89,0:56:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒\N{\fs14}Wake up.
